title: Vice to launch 12 channels in Europe, with a US network coming shortly
text:
Vice to launch 12 channels in Europe, with a US network coming shortly 
Published By: DigitalTrends.com - Today 
The media company has announced they will launch 12 channels on a variety of mobile, telcom, and terrestrial platforms in Europe next year. ...
